## Working with agents in this repo

This project uses a shared agent-coordination doc layer.

- **`AGENTS.md`** — routing rules every coding agent (Claude Code,
  Codex, Gemini, Aider, Cursor) reads on entry. `CLAUDE.md` /
  `GEMINI.md` / `AGENT.md` are aliases that resolve to it.
- **`.agent_works/`** — durable agent state (decisions, plans,
  requirements, handoff, work queue).
- **`.local/`** — gitignored scratch.

If you're an agent reading this, start with `AGENTS.md` and
`.agent_works/handoff/current_handoff.md`.
